ames like basketball, Nerf guns, and paper toss will. If you're expecting a 2-hour solo game, this probably isn't for you. However, if you plan to entertain your friends and family or want to draw a crowd, this is the perfect title.\n\nKey Detective Features:\n\n10 levels of puzzles\nMini-games to earn coins for clues (basketball, paper toss, Nerf guns)\nMore levels coming...\nKevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)\nLicensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0\nhttp://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/", "short_description": "The most obvious solutions are not the way out. Impossible Doors is designed to get you thinking outside the box in the shortest possible time. Enjoy these tricky levels!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://orangenose.notion.site/Core-Loop-526683c3424d473e8981689fc63f2b9b", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://app.getterms.io/view/wAH42/tos/en-us", "publisher_name": "Core Loop", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.coreloop.fun/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "377978390272490"}, {"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7911962568857851"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "948985519885235"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "948985519885235"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1724756340, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "948985519885235"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes